  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add chicken and cook until browned, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Add diced potatoes, corn kernels, flour, and chicken broth. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 15-20 minutes.",
